Changelog
=========

* `1.0.1`_ (3-Jan-2015)

  - Switch from using drone.io to travis-ci.org

* `1.0.0`_ (3-Jan-2015)

  - Update metadata version based on tag and git repo state.
  - Write local version to file when `--version-file` is specified.

